file.name: objects-test.yml
file.content:
components:
  schemas:
    # String
    ko_wild: &wild
      description: lacks everything
      type: object
    ko_wild_1:
      <<: *wild
      additionalProperties: true
    ko_wild_2: &wild_2
      <<: *wild
      description: |-
        jsonschema draft-6 supports http://json-schema.org/understanding-json-schema/reference/object.html
        propertyNames:
          pattern: "[a-z]+"
      additionalProperties:
        type: string
        maxLength: 8
        format: date
    ok_wild_3:
      <<: *wild_2
      maxProperties: 3
    ok_object:
      type: object
      additionalProperties: false
      properties:
        a:
          type: string
          maxLength: 8
          format: date
    ok_nested_object:
      type: object
      maxProperties: 1
      additionalProperties:
        type: object
        maxProperties: 1
        additionalProperties:
          type: string
          maxLength: 8

openapi: 3.0.1
paths:
  /string-ko-params:
    parameters:
      - name: ko_1
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: ciao
